      "index": "z00009",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "handler sse.StreamOrderMonitor → MonitorSnapshot → buildMonitorPayloads\non connect: Subscribe order:<id> · queue:broadcast · tables:broadcast → emit 'connected'\ninitial snapshot: 1×queue.update + 1×tables.status  · keep-alive comment every 15s\n⚠ NO per-order ownership check — only validates non-empty :id (asymmetry vs REST)\nListActiveOrders + ListTables on connect; pub/sub is TRANSPORT only, not a cache",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "handler sse.StreamOrderMonitor → MonitorSnapshot → buildMonitorPayloads\non connect: Subscribe order:<id> · queue:broadcast · tables:broadcast → emit 'connected'\ninitial snapshot: 1×queue.update + 1×tables.status  · keep-alive comment every 15s\n⚠ NO per-order ownership check — only validates non-empty :id (asymmetry vs REST)\nListActiveOrders + ListTables on connect; pub/sub is TRANSPORT only, not a cache",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
